## 3. Conformity statement

The provider declares that the high-risk AI system identified above is **in conformity** with the relevant Union harmonisation legislation, specifically:

- Regulation (EU) 2024/1689 (Artificial Intelligence Act), Chapters III (Title III, high-risk AI systems) and IV (transparency obligations), and the obligations of providers under Article 16.

## 4. References to harmonised standards or common specifications

Where harmonised standards have not yet been formally adopted, the provider applies the following common specifications and codes of practice:

- ISO/IEC 42001:2023 (AI management systems) - aspirational alignment.
- ISO/IEC 23894:2023 (AI risk management) - aspirational alignment.
- NIST AI Risk Management Framework v1.0 - guidance only.

